-- U.S. Says It Will Charge Three Hedge Fund Managers in New York
-- B y   D a v i d   E .   R o v e l l a
-- 2011-02-08T14:46:38Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-08/three-hedge-fund-managers-to-be-charged-by-u-s-prosecutors-in-manhattan.html
Three hedge fund portfolio managers
and one hedge fund analyst will be charged by federal
prosecutors in Manhattan, the government said. Two of the fund
managers face counts of obstruction of justice, according to a
statement today by the office of U.S. Attorney Preet Bharara in  Manhattan . A press conference is scheduled for noon.  To contact the reporter on this story:
